Here's a full list of the tools available to me:

## 🗂️ File System Tools
- `read_text_file` / `read_multiple_files` - Read file contents
- `write_file` - Create or overwrite files
- `edit_file` - Make line-based edits to files
- `list_directory` - List files in a directory
- `directory_tree` - Recursive tree view of files
- `search_files` - Find files by pattern
- `create_directory` - Create directories
- `move_file` - Move or rename files
- `get_file_info` - Get file metadata (size, dates, etc.)
- `read_media_file` - Read images/audio as base64
- `list_allowed_directories` - See which directories I can access

## 🔧 Git Tools
- `git_status` / `git_diff` / `git_diff_staged` / `git_diff_unstaged` - Check repo state
- `git_add` / `git_reset` - Stage/unstage changes
- `git_commit` - Commit changes
- `git_branch` / `git_checkout` / `git_create_branch` - Branch operations
- `git_log` / `git_show` - View history

## 🔍 Web Search Tools
- `search` (DuckDuckGo) - Search the web
- `fetch_content` - Read full webpage content

## ⏰ Time Tools
- `get_current_time` - Get current time in any timezone
- `convert_time` - Convert time between timezones

## 📚 RAG / Document Tools (Image Sets library)
- `rag_list_libraries` - List available RAG libraries
- `rag_search` - Search for documents
- `rag_get_document` - Get document content
- `rag_write_document_to_drive` - Write documents to drive
- `rag_ingest_generated_document` - Ingest new documents

## 💾 Artifact Memory
- `artifact_memory_get_index` - List saved artifacts
- `artifact_memory_get_latest` - Get most recent version
- `artifact_memory_list_versions` - View version history

## ⚡ Other
- `powershell_execute` - Run PowerShell commands
- `sequentialthinking` - Structured problem-solving

Is there something specific you'd like me to help with using these tools? 🙂


