**Features:**
- 🎯 **Animated needle** that wobbles randomly to simulate fluctuating pressure
- 🟢 **Green safe zone** (0-60 PSI)
- 🟡 **Yellow warning zone** (60-80 PSI)  
- 🔴 **Red danger zone** (80-100 PSI)
- ✨ **Glowing effects** on the needle and center hub
- 📊 **Major and minor tick marks** with labeled PSI values

The needle animates with a breathing wobble effect - it shifts position randomly every few seconds to simulate pressure fluctuations. Open this in a browser to see the animation!


