`type="rotate" values="angle cx cy; angle cx cy; ..."`

So the correct format should be:
`type="rotate" values="-35 150 150; -25 150 150; -40 150 150; ..."`

Or I can wrap the needle in a group that has a transform with the rotation center set, and then animate within that.

