[assistant]: <think>The user is saying the needle is still not rotating around the center. The issue is that SVG's `animateTransform` with type="rotate" doesn't automatically use the center as the rotation point unless you specify it.

The format for animateTransform with rotation is:
`<animateTransform attributeName="transform" type="rotate" values="angle1; angle2; ..." dur="Xs" repeatCount="indefinite"/>`

